snippet.title: Patchman vs. Red Circles
snippet.description:
It's Patchman against the Red Circles in the first episode of the indie epic "Don't Be Patchman"!  Who is Patchman and why shouldn't you be him?  And what are those red circles all about?  For Windows, Mac, Linux, Android, and iOS!

Steam: http://steam.dontbe.ca
Android: http://android.dontbe.ca
iOS: http://ios.dontbe.ca
itch.io: http://itch.dontbe.ca
